{"tid":433604,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"樂器老師係咪傾向唔教樂理架？","createTime":"2017-10-12T13:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T14:28:56.000Z","uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8995a75e9aaaeeb0e3a3e0c25fc923120f5a7167","tid":433604,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"跟左個老師學左年半結他<br />\n但係只係識睇五線譜既拍子<br />\n有份六線譜擺係前面係識彈既<br />\n但係如果得鋼琴譜既話就淨係譜彈melody一粒一粒音彈出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同朋友一齊夾就淨係識9掃chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明練過好多riff但係冇譜就唔識用番出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下惡補樂理對我喱個情況有冇用<br />\n我唔想淨係搵人地既譜黎彈<br />\n得應該點樣著手去學"},{"pid":"9acd70e0d9b81964b78c6ad60e55ec857d05fe28","tid":433604,"uid":60410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"佢冇料"},{"pid":"a09287b66f0b20a96184f1a54e10d94969d5eb82","tid":433604,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢冇料</blockquote><br />\n換老師"},{"pid":"1f692289ceeb798741f2b96760f9233477655eaf","tid":433604,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"結他老師。。。"},{"pid":"325dc47831f453f9119cc0cb47a5938dbde964cb","tid":433604,"uid":48504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"可能佢本身樂理都麻麻"}]}